This bit is resolved if we use the annotation this way:
@QuarkusTestResource(KeycloakQuarkusTestResource.Conditional.class)

This way the test resource will only be executed if there are some properties enabled. See more here: https://github.com/kiegroup/kogito-runtimes/tree/master/kogito-test-utils

